definition: to cut short/extinct/to disappear/to vanish/absolutely/by no means
abbr. for 非洲[Fei1 zhou1], Africa
to not be/not/wrong/incorrect/non-/un-/in-/to reproach or blame/(colloquial) to insist on/simply must

sentences.english: She has the beauty that beggars description.
sentences.chinese: 她的美貌絕非筆墨所能形容。

sentences.english: For example, honeybees are great builders. Beehive construction begins with finding a suitable site.
sentences.chinese: 事實上，蜜蜂是偉大的建築師，而絕非僅僅是蜇人。

sentences.english: I didn't break it on purpose, Mum, it was an accident!
sentences.chinese: 他的死絕非僅僅偶然事故所致，而是壞人有意策劃的。

sentences.english: But we even find it hard to beat them when we’re at home”.
sentences.chinese: 但即使是在主場，擊敗希洪也絕非易事。

sentences.english: Some say this is no coincidence.
It was not brought about by accident, but by the malice of Cupid (Eros).
sentences.chinese: 事情的發生絕非偶然，而是邱比特故意搞的鬼。

sentences.english: But no one became Roman overnight.
sentences.chinese: 但轉化爲羅馬人絕非一夕之功。

sentences.english: Certainly the phenomenon of sexuality-in-flux is by no means exclusive to women.
sentences.chinese: 當然性傾向在同量的情況下絕非排斥女性。

sentences.english: This small"demon"not wave get hollow reputation.
sentences.chinese: 這個小“精靈”絕非浪得虛名。

sentences.english: In which, it's not as easy as the so called "popularity of Sinology" can explain it.
sentences.chinese: 這其中，絕非是所謂的國學熱這麼簡單可以解釋的。

sentences.english: Whatever else is unsure in this stinking dunghill of a world a mother's love is not.
sentences.chinese: 母親之愛絕非是惡臭糞坑般的世界所無法確定的東西。

sentences.english: Sovereign default is far from inconceivable.
sentences.chinese: 主權國拖欠債務也絕非天方夜譚。

sentences.english: Art cannot rival this pomp of purple and gold.
sentences.chinese: 浮華的金紫，絕非畫師所能描繪。

sentences.english: Failure should be our teacher, not our undertaker.
sentences.chinese: 失敗是我們的老師，而絕非掘墓人。

sentences.english: The reason why Lu Xun named his essay collections of "wild grass" is by no means accidental.
sentences.chinese: 散文詩集《野草》被魯迅命名爲“野草”絕非偶然。

sentences.english: Quintana is a crafty southpaw with good skills and is by no means a walk - over.
sentences.chinese: 昆塔納是個技術出色的狡猾的左撇子，絕非等閒之輩。
